Net-CyanChat version 0.06
=========================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  strict
  warnings
  IO::Socket
  IO::Select

EXAMPLES

A couple example scripts can be found in the "eg" folder:

  ccserver - A simple CyanChat server.
  tcc      - A less-than-simple CyanChat client.

